{"tid":2379394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"技術員被控雨傘襲警惟影片拍不到 督察自言英國讀書 中文「麻麻」未能讀出被告中文全名","createTime":"2021-01-25T08:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T10:10:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e59b295b2f84a646aa47d0f706d3603e2ce37ff","tid":2379394,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"前年7月14日有團體在沙田發起遊行，演變成警民衝突，警方進入新城市廣場掃蕩，有電腦技術員被指用雨傘打督察雙手。涉案技術員今就襲警罪受審，庭上播出案發影片，督察同意影片拍不到他所供稱的事發經過，但強調是「剛剛之前一秒（發生）」。辯方指被告當時遭胡椒噴霧波及，「揈」雨傘阻擋噴霧，根本沒襲擊督察，因此督察沒有驗傷，亦沒有為傷勢拍照作紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n事發時將被告按在地上的督察葉浩明今午作供，解釋因在英國讀書，讀及寫中文均「麻麻」，未能讀出被告中文全名。葉表示，被告被制服後稱雙眼灼痛，他遂拿出清水由同袍為被告清洗雙眼。<br />\n<br />\n警員9272翟浩權（音）事後以襲警罪名拘捕被告，在被告褲袋內找到黑噴漆，另在被告背囊內找到生理鹽水、電筒及黑色雨傘等物。翟接受辯方盤問時同意，遇襲督察向他講述事發經過，督察又稱沒有傷勢，故沒有驗傷。<br />\n<br />\n辯方問翟，他有沒有叫報稱受傷的督察就襲警事件做紀錄，翟稱相信督察會自行記錄，惟翟同意本案最終沒有受傷照片或醫療報告。裁判官香淑嫻裁定案件表證成立，被告不作供，亦不傳召辯方證人。案件明早結案陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/KAUG756L7RF53KAOK2AQE3SZIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FKAUG756L7RF53KAOK2AQE3SZIA%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=7d19f79f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FKAUG756L7RF53KAOK2AQE3SZIA%2F&h=67995b4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/KAUG756L7RF53KAOK2AQE3SZIA/</a>"},{"pid":"f0d0e667aa5bedb6a45ef8940bf77fec37faea8c","tid":2379394,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57765e46e2643d013d09f9f76642ac0eff5220d3","tid":2379394,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:31:28.000Z","msg":"香淑X<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72825b5c0b2689bea8579d0af271377552e7ada5","tid":2379394,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:10:22.000Z","msg":"去年 7 月沙田大遊行中，一名 26 歲電腦技術員被指以雨傘敲打督察雙手一下，遭控襲警罪。案件今（ 25 日）於沙田法院開審，報稱被襲的督察霍建文同意現場片段拍不到事發經過，但強調在開拍前一秒發生。他又指被襲後感痛楚，但卻沒有前往醫院驗傷。另一督察葉浩明在宣誓時，曾一度不懂讀「謹此宣誓」的「謹」字，他解釋自己在英國讀書，故「讀同寫（中文）都麻麻」。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/7-14-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%82%E8%AE%80-%E8%AC%B9-%E5%AD%97-%E7%A8%B1%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%AE%80%E6%9B%B8%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-%E9%BA%BB%E9%BA%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-14-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%259D%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2582%25E8%25AE%2580-%25E8%25AC%25B9-%25E5%25AD%2597-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AE%2580%25E6%259B%25B8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587-%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E9%25BA%25BB%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=7c7f1090\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-14-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%259D%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2582%25E8%25AE%2580-%25E8%25AC%25B9-%25E5%25AD%2597-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AE%2580%25E6%259B%25B8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587-%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E9%25BA%25BB%2F&h=7641cc35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/7-14-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%82%E8%AE%80-%E8%AC%B9-%E5%AD%97-%E7%A8%B1%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%AE%80%E6%9B%B8%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-%E9%BA%BB%E9%BA%BB/</a>"}]}